Package com.foley.graph.core

Interface Graph<V,​E>

Type Parameters:
V - The type of vertices in the graph
E - The type of cost between vertices in the graph
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractGraph, BasicGraph, BasicHashGraph
public interface Graph<V,​E>
An abstract, unordered collection of vertices and the edges relating them
